More Life Esidimeni missing patients have been found by the Gauteng Health Department. MEC Gwen Ramokgopa visited some of the families on Sunday. The last count had indicated that 48 patients were unaccounted for by the end of the Arbitration Hearings. Speaking from Lenasia, while visiting some of the families, MEC Ramokgopa said, “From the list we could account for those that went to the NGOs, those that went to the Acute Hospitals and many others.”  More below: 